text.text: Move Chat History from Other Apps

text:
• Move your message history from other apps such as WhatsApp, Line and KakaoTalk to Telegram.
• Use the Export Chat function in the other app, then Share the exported file to Telegram (see blog post for detailed instructions).

• Delete messages, groups you created, secret chats, and call history for all sides, without a trace.

More about this update:
